dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Map shows two classes of roads, trails, and four classes of towns. Map includes glossary of abbreviations. "Compiled by the Army Map Service May 1943, from the following sources; Isola di Rodi, 1:100,000, Istituto Geografico Militare, 1931-Anno IX. Dodecanese 1:100,000, Rhodes, 512 (A.Fd.Svy.), 1941). "A.M.S. 6201." "For use by War and Navy Department Agencies only. Not for sale or distribution." "302029 - 3/45 ED."
